‐ Nice to see you.
‐ Huh!

00:02:30.450 --> 00:02:31.485
Professor Sycamore?

00:02:33.553 --> 00:02:35.922
'What are you doing here,
professor?'

00:02:35.922 --> 00:02:37.891
There's only one reason for me
to be away from my lab.

