on Mega Evolution, right?

00:02:43.463 --> 00:02:47.067
Still as perceptive as ever,
Clemont. Exactly.

00:02:47.067 --> 00:02:49.369
I'm doing extensive research
on Diantha's Gardevoir

00:02:49.369 --> 00:02:51.705
and its Mega Evolution.

00:02:51.705 --> 00:02:54.241
‐ Oh!
‐ Wow, Gardevoir?

00:02:54.241 --> 00:02:56.476
‐ It can really Mega Evolve?
‐ It sure can!

00:02:56.476 --> 00:02:58.745
Wow. I wanna see!

00:02:58.745 --> 00:03:00.914
Have you already seen Diantha,
professor?

00:03:00.914 --> 00:03:03.116
‐ I have.
‐ Huh?

00:03:03.116 --> 00:03:03.784
PROFESSOR SYCAMORE
She's getting her makeup done

00:03:03.784 --> 00:03:05.318
in the next room.

00:03:05.318 --> 00:03:06.787
ASH SERENA BONNIE CLEMONT
Oh!

00:03:06.787 --> 00:03:08.955
Diantha's on the other side
of that door!

00:03:08.955 --> 00:03:11.058
Wow, wow, wow!

00:03:11.058 --> 00:03:13.894
We are so unbelievably lucky!

00:03:13.894 --> 00:03:17.297
Yes! I'm gonna go challenge her
to a battle!

00:03:17.297 --> 00:03:19.466
Sorry to keep you waiting,
professor.

00:03:19.466 --> 00:03:22.235
Oh, dear, I see you have guests,
don't you?

00:03:22.235 --> 00:03:24.171
‐ Oh. It's Diantha for real.
‐ Oh.

00:03:24.171 --> 00:03:26.006
So pretty!

00:03:26.006 --> 00:03:28.408
[chuckles]
Why, thank you.

00:03:28.408 --> 00:03:32.813
So, did you reconsider what
we spoke about earlier, Diantha?

00:03:32.813 --> 00:03:36.249
