[STUNNED]

00:08:16.062 --> 00:08:17.731
ANNOUNCER
Absol is unable to battle,

00:08:17.731 --> 00:08:19.666
Gardevoir's the winner.

00:08:19.666 --> 00:08:22.135
'Which means, the victory goes
to Diantha.'

00:08:22.135 --> 00:08:24.270
‐ Incredible.
‐ Diantha's amazing.

00:08:24.270 --> 00:08:26.306
‐ Wonderful.
‐ She's strong.

00:08:26.306 --> 00:08:28.241
‐ Gardevoir didn't Mega Evolve.
‐ And they still won.

00:08:28.241 --> 00:08:29.776
Awesome!

00:08:29.776 --> 00:08:32.679
[crowd applauding]

00:08:32.679 --> 00:08:35.181
Yeah! I'm gonna get her
to battle me!

00:08:35.181 --> 00:08:38.952
I'll ask her again, too.
For my research.

00:08:38.952 --> 00:08:40.720
MAN #2
Will she comment on her victory?

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:41.821
‐ Just a few words?
‐ Whoa!

00:08:41.821 --> 00:08:43.623
They're all here again.

