It says they make the best
chocolate cake anywhere.

00:09:02.776 --> 00:09:04.711
‐ Let's find out.
‐ I wanna go too.

00:09:04.711 --> 00:09:06.246
Sounds great.

00:09:06.246 --> 00:09:08.348
Would you like to come,
professor?

00:09:08.348 --> 00:09:11.551
Sure do! First, I have to send
the footage to the research lab.

