Huh! Diantha?

00:10:57.390 --> 00:10:58.558
PIKACHU/DEDENNE
[SHOCKED]

00:10:58.558 --> 00:11:00.193
Shh.

00:11:00.193 --> 00:11:02.028
[chuckles]

00:11:02.028 --> 00:11:03.229
GROUP
Who's that Pokémon?

00:11:08.935 --> 00:11:10.303
GROUP
It's Gardevoir!

00:11:10.303 --> 00:11:11.504
[PROUD]

00:11:17.210 --> 00:11:17.944
CLEMONT
'Now, where were we?'

00:11:21.381 --> 00:11:23.783
‐ Alright.
‐ Science is so amazing.

00:11:23.783 --> 00:11:25.852
[AGREEMENT]

00:11:25.852 --> 00:11:28.354
‐ 'Help yourself, Diantha.'
‐ 'Thank you.'

00:11:28.354 --> 00:11:29.589
ASH/SERENA/BONNIE/CLEMONT
'Let's eat!'

00:11:29.589 --> 00:11:31.224
‐ Mm..
‐ Mm.

00:11:31.224 --> 00:11:32.859
‐ Mmm.
‐ Mmm.

00:11:32.859 --> 00:11:34.594
Mmm.

00:11:34.594 --> 00:11:36.863
‐ So good!
‐ So good!

00:11:36.863 --> 00:11:39.599
Wow, best chocolate cake
I ever had.

00:11:39.599 --> 00:11:42.936
It is, the sweetness brings
the bold bitterness

00:11:42.936 --> 00:11:46.539
and acidity together perfectly,
a memorable cake, for sure.

00:11:46.539 --> 00:11:50.176
‐ You certainly know your cake.
‐ I just adore desserts.

00:11:50.176 --> 00:11:52.278
‐ I do, too.
‐ Me too.

00:11:52.278 --> 00:11:54.380
DEDENNE
[HAPPY]

00:11:54.380 --> 00:11:57.350
Whenever I visit a town
for work, I always look forward

00:11:57.350 --> 00:11:59.118
to sampling their most
popular desserts

00:11:59.118 --> 00:12:01.020
whether I'm busy or not.

00:12:01.020 --> 00:12:02.722
CLEMONT
Movie star and Champion,

00:12:02.722 --> 00:12:04.524
juggling two jobs

00:12:04.524 --> 00:12:06.159
must be challenging,
to say the least.

00:12:06.159 --> 00:12:08.528
But I do it out of love

00:12:08.528 --> 00:12:10.430
so, it's really not work at all.

00:12:10.430 --> 00:12:12.065
You're so amazing.

00:12:12.065 --> 00:12:15.168
That's right, you're a keeper.
He‐he‐he!

00:12:15.168 --> 00:12:18.571
Won't you please,
take care of my brother?

00:12:18.571 --> 00:12:21.341
‐ Take care?
‐ I told you to stop this!

00:12:21.341 --> 00:12:23.676
You see,
my brother is a bit shy.

00:12:23.676 --> 00:12:25.378
So, I thought it would be good

00:12:25.378 --> 00:12:28.081
if he married
a dependable woman like you.

00:12:28.081 --> 00:12:30.283
Me? Marry your brother?

00:12:30.283 --> 00:12:32.018
[chuckles]
It was a joke.

00:12:32.018 --> 00:12:33.886
I wasn't joking!

00:12:33.886 --> 00:12:35.888
Excuse me, Diantha?

00:12:35.888 --> 00:12:37.357
Please have
a Pokémon battle with me.

00:12:37.357 --> 00:12:39.092
Huh, you?

00:12:39.092 --> 00:12:41.327
‐ Ash!
‐ Huh?

00:12:41.327 --> 00:12:43.997
You must know Diantha
doesn't get much private time

00:12:43.997 --> 00:12:46.532
and here you are bothering her
this way.

00:12:46.532 --> 00:12:49.869
Yeah, but..
I want to be a Pokémon Master.

00:12:49.869 --> 00:12:51.871
So, having a battle with you
would be awesome.

00:12:51.871 --> 00:12:53.606
'Because you're the Champion.
Please?'

00:12:59.445 --> 00:13:02.148
‐ Alright.
‐ Huh?

00:13:02.148 --> 00:13:05.251
I usually turn down unofficial
battle requests

00:13:05.251 --> 00:13:07.787
but, you shared your chocolate
cake with me, just this once.

00:13:07.787 --> 00:13:09.656
Alright she said yes, Pikachu!

00:13:09.656 --> 00:13:11.758
[EXCITED]

00:13:11.758 --> 00:13:13.726
'A battle against
the Champion, eh?'

00:13:13.726 --> 00:13:16.362
SERENA
Professor.

00:13:16.362 --> 00:13:18.031
If you don't mind,
I'd like to come watch it.

00:13:23.169 --> 00:13:24.671
I see you're going to use
Pikachu..

00:13:24.671 --> 00:13:25.972
‐ Right?
‐ Right.

00:13:25.972 --> 00:13:28.207
[EXCITED]

00:13:28.207 --> 00:13:30.943
Now, I really hope to see
a Mega Evolution this time.

00:13:30.943 --> 00:13:32.812
Battle begin!

00:13:36.683 --> 00:13:39.118
‐ You may go first, Ash.
‐ Pikachu, use Iron Tail.

00:13:39.118 --> 00:13:42.121
[IRON TAIL MOVE]

00:13:42.121 --> 00:13:43.990
GARDEVOIR
[DODGING]

00:13:43.990 --> 00:13:45.591
Now, follow it
with Quick Attack.

00:13:45.591 --> 00:13:47.994
[QUICK ATTACK MOVE]

00:13:47.994 --> 00:13:50.229
GARDEVOIR/PIKACHU
[DODGING]/[QUICK ATTACK MOVE]

00:13:50.229 --> 00:13:51.731
Use Electro Ball.

00:13:51.731 --> 00:13:52.865
[ELECTRO BALL MOVE]

00:13:52.865 --> 00:13:54.200
[AFFIRMATIVE]/[DODGING]

00:13:54.200 --> 00:13:55.601
Now, Thunderbolt.

00:13:55.601 --> 00:13:57.937
[THUNDERBOLT MOVE]

00:13:59.605 --> 00:14:01.674
GARDEVOIR
[DODGING]

00:14:01.674 --> 00:14:03.042
Huh, wow, it dodged
Thunderbolt, too..

00:14:03.042 --> 00:14:04.677
[SHOCKED]

00:14:04.677 --> 00:14:06.612
Pikachu's moves
didn't do a thing!

00:14:06.612 --> 00:14:09.148
‐ Wow!
‐ And checkmate.

00:14:09.148 --> 00:14:10.850
Shadow Ball, go!

00:14:10.850 --> 00:14:12.385
[SHADOW BALL MOVE]

00:14:14.053 --> 00:14:16.022
PIKACHU
[PANIC]/[PAINED]

00:14:16.022 --> 00:14:17.590
Pikachu!

00:14:17.590 --> 00:14:19.926
[panting]

00:14:19.926 --> 00:14:22.962
[grunting]

00:14:22.962 --> 00:14:26.165
‐ Ash!
‐ Oh, man, that hurt.

00:14:26.165 --> 00:14:28.101
But I'm fine.
Hey, buddy, are you okay, too?

00:14:28.101 --> 00:14:29.936
[REASSURING]

00:14:29.936 --> 00:14:32.839
'Alright, the real battle
starts now.'

00:14:32.839 --> 00:14:33.840
[thinking]
He really cares

00:14:33.840 --> 00:14:35.775
about his Pokémon.

00:14:35.775 --> 00:14:39.178
Ash is a very passionate
Trainer.

00:14:39.178 --> 00:14:40.279
GARDEVOIR
[SURPRISED]

00:14:40.279 --> 00:14:42.415
[all gasping]

00:14:42.415 --> 00:14:44.617
Prepare for trouble,
actress to actress.

00:14:44.617 --> 00:14:47.153
But two are too many,
so more is really less.

00:14:47.153 --> 00:14:49.589
To protect the world
from competition.

00:14:49.589 --> 00:14:52.291
In keeping
with the actor's tradition.

00:14:52.291 --> 00:14:54.961
To perform with great style,
truth and love.

00:14:54.961 --> 00:14:58.765
To allow great talent
to fit like a glove.

00:14:58.765 --> 00:15:01.033
‐ Jessie!
‐ And James!

00:15:01.033 --> 00:15:02.335
JESSIE
Team Rocket blasts off

00:15:02.335 --> 00:15:03.836
with award‐winning grace.

00:15:03.836 --> 00:15:05.304
JAMES
Surrender now or prepare

00:15:05.304 --> 00:15:06.606
for us in your face!

00:15:06.606 --> 00:15:07.774
Meowth, on the case!

00:15:09.876 --> 00:15:13.112
[PANIC]

00:15:13.112 --> 00:15:15.415
Team Rocket!
You're doing it again?

00:15:15.415 --> 00:15:17.417
They're a bunch of
really bad guys

00:15:17.417 --> 00:15:19.685
who go around stealing
other people's Pokémon.

00:15:19.685 --> 00:15:23.022
They steal Pokémon?
What despicable people!

00:15:23.022 --> 00:15:26.592
Why, thank you, we'll wear
that as a badge of honor.

00:15:26.592 --> 00:15:28.461
Since I'm the greatest actress
of all time

00:15:28.461 --> 00:15:30.062
I accept your kind words.

00:15:30.062 --> 00:15:31.731
Quick, Gardevoir, Shadow Ball.

00:15:31.731 --> 00:15:33.433
[SHADOW BALL MOVE]

00:15:35.635 --> 00:15:37.703
Oh, smashing.

00:15:37.703 --> 00:15:39.472
The only thing
getting in and out of this box

00:15:39.472 --> 00:15:40.640
is sunlight, dig!

00:15:40.640 --> 00:15:43.376
And, curtain up!

00:15:43.376 --> 00:15:45.478
[all screaming]

00:15:45.478 --> 00:15:47.413
MEOWTH
Bye‐bye, chump guys!

00:15:47.413 --> 00:15:49.916
[coughing]

00:15:49.916 --> 00:15:52.418
‐ Ah, they're gone.
‐ They flew away.

00:15:52.418 --> 00:15:55.621
Don't worry,
I'll take us right to them.

00:15:55.621 --> 00:15:57.323
PROFESSOR SYCAMORE
Diantha, wait, do you know

00:15:57.323 --> 00:15:59.025
where Gardevoir is?

00:15:59.025 --> 00:15:59.926
Yes.

00:16:05.364 --> 00:16:07.133
[panting]

00:16:07.133 --> 00:16:10.136
BONNIE
Come on, Clemont, hurry up!

00:16:10.136 --> 00:16:11.871
It happened when I was
in the Lapidarian Highlands

00:16:11.871 --> 00:16:13.973
for a film shoot.

00:16:13.973 --> 00:16:16.175
Whoa! That's one of the last
unexplored regions in the world.

00:16:16.175 --> 00:16:18.644
Yes, that's right.

00:16:18.644 --> 00:16:20.246
A thick fog
rolled into the area

00:16:20.246 --> 00:16:20.913
while we were shooting.

00:16:22.815 --> 00:16:23.850
Huh.

00:16:27.787 --> 00:16:28.688
Huh?

00:16:39.332 --> 00:16:41.133
It's Gardevoir.

00:16:41.133 --> 00:16:42.301
[HAPPY]

00:16:44.737 --> 00:16:46.439
KATHI LEE
Diantha!

00:16:46.439 --> 00:16:49.609
[CALM]

00:16:49.609 --> 00:16:51.177
DIANTHA
Later, my manager Kathi Lee

00:16:51.177 --> 00:16:52.712
told me that Gardevoir

00:16:52.712 --> 00:16:55.481
had appeared
from its Poké Ball on its own.

00:16:55.481 --> 00:16:58.918
It then guided everyone to
exactly where I had gotten lost.

00:16:58.918 --> 00:17:01.354
Hm, could the stones be
responsible for what happened?

00:17:01.354 --> 00:17:03.389
I wonder..

00:17:03.389 --> 00:17:05.324
Maybe Diantha's and Gardevoir's
hearts were connected

00:17:05.324 --> 00:17:07.159
and called out to each other.

00:17:07.159 --> 00:17:09.362
Did you say it was our hearts?

00:17:09.362 --> 00:17:11.597
‐ I think Ash is right.
‐ Yup.

00:17:11.597 --> 00:17:14.333
Hmm, huh?

00:17:14.333 --> 00:17:15.167
Gardevoir's up ahead.

00:17:16.802 --> 00:17:19.138
‐ Huh?
‐ Huh?

00:17:19.138 --> 00:17:20.006
ASH
It's them!

00:17:22.608 --> 00:17:25.912
So, let's review, this Gardevoir
can Mega Evolve.

00:17:25.912 --> 00:17:28.080
And once it's safely
into the Boss's hands

00:17:28.080 --> 00:17:29.482
we'll evolve into big shots.

00:17:29.482 --> 00:17:31.684
A major mega‐promotion!

00:17:31.684 --> 00:17:34.253
[laughing]

00:17:34.253 --> 00:17:35.154
JESSIE/JAMES
'Hey!'

00:17:35.154 --> 00:17:36.956
There they are..

00:17:36.956 --> 00:17:38.858
Ash, I want you all
to stay here.

00:17:38.858 --> 00:17:40.493
‐ Uh, but..
‐ It'll be fine.

00:17:42.795 --> 00:17:45.698
Alright, you listen.

00:17:45.698 --> 00:17:48.367
I want my Gardevoir.

00:17:48.367 --> 00:17:51.404
‐ How'd she find us?
‐ Ha! The how means nothing!

00:17:51.404 --> 00:17:54.874
We'll just see, now, Gardevoir!

00:17:54.874 --> 00:17:56.943
Let's show them a few things
about a strong bond.

00:17:58.411 --> 00:17:59.278
[AFFIRMATIVE]

00:18:06.085 --> 00:18:08.821
[EXERTION]

00:18:13.759 --> 00:18:16.362
‐ Look at that light..
‐ Is it..

00:18:16.362 --> 00:18:18.798
It is! That's when a Pokémon
Mega Evolves.

00:18:18.798 --> 00:18:21.300
Gardevoir, now Mega Evolve!

00:18:21.300 --> 00:18:23.936
[EVOLVING]

00:18:35.748 --> 00:18:38.818
[PROUD]

00:18:38.818 --> 00:18:41.420
‐ Yeah, check it out!
‐ Wow! It Mega Evolved!

00:18:41.420 --> 00:18:43.189
‐ What a sight.
‐ Excellent.

00:18:43.189 --> 00:18:45.625
‐ It's so coo.
‐ Marvelous.

00:18:45.625 --> 00:18:47.460
JESSIE
Uh, I think we're in trouble.

00:18:47.460 --> 00:18:48.961
MEOWTH
Chill! Our box can deal with

00:18:48.961 --> 00:18:50.896
'anything
that galoot dishes out!'

00:18:50.896 --> 00:18:52.898
Use Shadow Ball.

00:18:52.898 --> 00:18:54.433
[SHADOW BALL MOVE]

00:18:56.268 --> 00:18:57.837
[explosion]

00:18:57.837 --> 00:18:58.738
[screaming]

00:19:01.474 --> 00:19:04.777
‐ Our box is junk.
‐ Such pompous power.

00:19:04.777 --> 00:19:06.879
And checkmate!
Excellent work.

00:19:06.879 --> 00:19:08.714
Use Moon Blast.

00:19:08.714 --> 00:19:10.583
[MOON BLAST MOVE]

00:19:12.952 --> 00:19:15.154
‐ Let's beat a hasty retreat.
‐ Step on it.

00:19:15.154 --> 00:19:17.189
[MOON BLAST MOVE]

00:19:19.992 --> 00:19:22.428
JESSIE/JAMES/MEOWTH
We're blasting off again!

00:19:24.730 --> 00:19:26.165
‐ Awesome!
‐ You did it!

00:19:26.165 --> 00:19:28.601
[laughing]
[PROUD]

00:19:31.203 --> 00:19:33.205
‐ Huh?
‐ Hey, look, it changed back!

00:19:33.205 --> 00:19:35.508
Right, what makes
Mega Evolution different

00:19:35.508 --> 00:19:37.009
from ordinary Evolution
is it isn't permanent.

00:19:38.644 --> 00:19:41.047
[all gasping]

00:19:41.047 --> 00:19:42.415
That's what I call
perfect timing.

00:19:44.050 --> 00:19:45.785
Diantha!

00:19:45.785 --> 00:19:46.786
[chuckles]

00:19:50.122 --> 00:19:53.059
Ash, I realize
we weren't able to

00:19:53.059 --> 00:19:55.327
finish our battle together,
but it was fun.

00:19:55.327 --> 00:19:56.762
I thought it was fun, too!

00:19:56.762 --> 00:19:57.997
PIKACHU
[AFFIRMATIVE]

00:19:57.997 --> 00:20:00.566
Thanks so much to all of you.

00:20:00.566 --> 00:20:02.101
SERENA
Will we ever see you again?

00:20:02.101 --> 00:20:04.737
BONNIE
I wanna talk to you more.

00:20:04.737 --> 00:20:06.472
Now, you shouldn't bother her
like that!

00:20:06.472 --> 00:20:07.473
DIANTHA
I'm sorry. I have a movie shoot

00:20:07.473 --> 00:20:09.575
to get to.

00:20:09.575 --> 00:20:11.944
I want to thank you for showing
me the bond that's so crucial

00:20:11.944 --> 00:20:14.180
for a Pokémon to Mega Evolve.

00:20:14.180 --> 00:20:16.515
I'm glad I was able to help.
Take care!

00:20:19.418 --> 00:20:22.588
ASH
Diantha?

00:20:22.588 --> 00:20:25.758
Right now, I'm training really
hard to enter the Kalos League!

00:20:25.758 --> 00:20:29.128
So, when I win,
will you battle with me again?

00:20:29.128 --> 00:20:32.064
That's a tall order!
But, that's the spirit.

00:20:32.064 --> 00:20:34.033
Yes! I look forward to it!

00:20:37.703 --> 00:20:38.671
NARRATOR
An encounter with Diantha

00:20:38.671 --> 00:20:40.372
has given our heroes

00:20:40.372 --> 00:20:42.742
and Professor Sycamore
a deeper look

00:20:42.742 --> 00:20:45.010
into the mysteries
of Mega Evolution!

00:20:45.010 --> 00:20:47.246
Now, it's off once again
to Shalour City

00:20:47.246 --> 00:20:49.281
as the journey continues!

00:20:56.122 --> 00:20:58.724
[theme music]

